room_title: Escape room "Day of the Dead" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Riverside
room_description:
ou and your friends, resting on a beautiful island in the Caribbean, accidentally discover a cave. Curiosity forces you to go inside and you find yourself in the underground temple of mysterious Aztecs, where bloody mystical rites are still held in the name of the Sun, which illuminated the church 500 years ago.

The team is divided into two parts of the temple. Carefully studying the hieroglyphs and drawings on the walls, you can find a way out of the primeval temple and leave it unscathed,
returning to the place that was torn out in the name of the Sun, by opening the door to the outside with the help of a ritual instrument!
